<p><strong>Every row is the same, so you see stripes going up.</strong></p>
<p><strong>How many gold blocks are in each row? Circle one:</strong> 1 · 2 · 3</p>
<p><strong>Which colour is there the most of? Circle one:</strong> gold · black · purple · green</p>
<p>Record <strong>one video</strong> (a phone is fine). Show two things:</p>
<p><strong>1 · Your code.</strong> Scroll through it. Say what each part does.</p>
<p><strong>2 · Your build.</strong> Point the camera. Name the colours and the stripes.</p>
